Package: VibeCodeR
Title: Integrate RStudioAPI With Large Language Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Howard Swerdfeger <hswerdfe@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Howard Swerdfeger <hswerdfe@gmail.com>
Description: Provides RStudio Add-ins that integrate the RStudio API with large language models. Includes a custom project template and tools for generating function skeletons, inserting Roxygen documentation, and streamlining code editing with interactive interfaces.
